{"article":{"id":900005515186,"url":"https://mackerelio.zendesk.com/api/v2/help_center/en-us/articles/900005515186.json","html_url":"https://support.mackerel.io/hc/en-us/articles/900005515186-Is-it-possible-to-integrate-alert-notifications-with-external-services-like-chats-","author_id":390085917472,"comments_disabled":true,"draft":false,"promoted":false,"position":0,"vote_sum":0,"vote_count":0,"section_id":4412620274329,"created_at":"2021-04-06T08:42:54Z","updated_at":"2021-12-21T03:51:26Z","name":"Is it possible to integrate alert notifications with external services like chats?","title":"Is it possible to integrate alert notifications with external services like chats?","source_locale":"ja","locale":"en-us","outdated":false,"outdated_locales":[],"edited_at":"2021-04-09T09:56:02Z","user_segment_id":null,"permission_group_id":1305651,"content_tag_ids":[],"label_names":[],"body":"\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eYes. Monitoring related alert notifications can be integrated with external services such as chats and more.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003eSupported services are as follows.\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://mackerel.io/docs/entry/howto/alerts/slack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eSlack\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://mackerel.io/docs/entry/howto/alerts/line\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eLINE\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\"\u003e（※LINE WORKS is not currently supported）\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://mackerel.io/docs/entry/howto/alerts/chatwork\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"\u003eChatwork\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level